        <actionDate>2009-02-10</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2009-02-23T22:41:38Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Social Security Benefits Fairness Act of 2009 - Amends title II (Old Age, Survivors and Disability Insurance) (OASDI) of the Social Security Act to provide that, if an OASDI recipient dies during the first 15 days of a month, the last payment of the monthly benefit for that month shall be half the usual benefit amount.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Social Security Benefits Fairness Act of 2009</title>
    <titles>
